      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRITTAIN ON FIRE (2) is a sprinter who thrives over these shorter races. Was a strong winner last time (17.74) over 312m at this track in a OPEN. Form at the trip excellent including 22 wins. Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in seven starts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. DIRTY DANCING (1) shapes well for this backing up a solid 18.20 win with success at this track over 312m last time, recording 18.15. Harder here but expected to feature again. BRAVE EMBER (5) had been in super honest form hitting the frame three times on end before finishing fourth (22.64) at this track last time. Has a strong winning record at this journey. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Has the ability to give this a shake. ENIGMA GO (4) hit the frame latest (22.50) when second at this track in a Free For All. Has already won three times from this draw.",
